As for me, I don=E2=80=99t plan on blocking the GPTBot crawler or any other=
 crawlers via my Robots.txt file. The high-minded reason is because my prim=
ary goal when I started Stratechery was to share my ideas; my only economic=
 goal was to match my tech industry salary. Contributing to AI feels in lin=
