china ) ; has anyone who cares already left the platform? I personally stil=
l use Zoom, because it continues to be the best performing video conference=
 software: it handles poor connections better than anyone else, and is the =
only screen-sharing software that doesn=E2=80=99t make my fans take off lik=
e a jet engine. This update, though, does make me question the extent to wh=
ich I am foolishly favoring day-to-day quality of life increases over secur=
